241
00:18:35,920 --> 00:18:38,200
and then take the fight
to her decks.

242
00:18:38,240 --> 00:18:40,760
<i>That fight will be the fight</i>
<i>of our lives,</i>

243
00:18:40,800 --> 00:18:43,080
<i>make no mistake.</i>

244
00:18:43,160 --> 00:18:46,080
But on the other side

245
00:18:46,160 --> 00:18:47,800
lies paradise.

246
00:18:50,880 --> 00:18:53,200
