the details one more time.

257
00:20:19,280 --> 00:20:21,560
The harbormaster's
name is Singer.

258
00:20:21,600 --> 00:20:23,240
The foreman's name is Smith.

259
00:20:23,320 --> 00:20:24,840
The warehouse manager's Clay,

260
00:20:24,920 --> 00:20:26,120
