261
00:20:26,200 --> 00:20:28,440
<i>Now if you don't let me</i>
<i>board my ship</i>

262
00:20:28,480 --> 00:20:29,960
<i>and leave this place,</i>
<i>none of it will matter</i>

263
00:20:30,040 --> 00:20:33,240
as the goods in my hold will be rotten
by the time I arrive.

264
00:20:33,280 --> 00:20:35,320
- Goodbye.
- Godspeed.

265
00:20:41,000 --> 00:20:42,680
I have to hand it to you,

266
00:20:42,720 --> 00:20:44,560
you said you'd rebuild things
here without your father,

267
00:20:44,600 --> 00:20:46,680
and damned if you
didn't do just that.

268
00:20:46,720 --> 00:20:49,040
Still one step
yet to accomplish.

269
00:20:51,040 --> 00:20:53,160
Removing my father entirely.

270
00:20:53,240 --> 00:20:54,520
Excuse me?

271
00:20:54,600 --> 00:20:56,200
