322
00:23:39,640 --> 00:23:41,360
Mr. Gates...

323
00:23:44,360 --> 00:23:45,800
<i>Sails!</i>

324
00:23:45,880 --> 00:23:47,320
To the south!

325
00:23:47,400 --> 00:23:49,000
