330
00:24:05,280 --> 00:24:06,840
In less than half an hour,
she'll be right on top of us.

331
00:24:06,880 --> 00:24:08,800
Get orders to the Ranger.

332
00:24:08,880 --> 00:24:10,560
Tell her to raise the black

333
00:24:10,640 --> 00:24:13,080
and fire two shots over our bow.

334
00:24:13,160 --> 00:24:15,280
- Mr. De Groot.
- <i>Captain?</i>

335
00:24:15,320 --> 00:24:17,400
<i>Rig a spring to the forward anchor,</i>
<i>then drop her immediately.</i>

336
00:24:17,480 --> 00:24:19,240
Drop anchor?

337
00:24:19,320 --> 00:24:20,840
You mean to fight her?

338
00:24:20,920 --> 00:24:22,800
You all have your orders!

339
00:24:27,760 --> 00:24:29,600
Captain, join me.

340
00:24:29,680 --> 00:24:32,240
- We don't have time.
- Make time.

341
00:24:37,960 --> 00:24:40,120
If he engages that ship
in battle, we're dead.

342
00:24:40,200 --> 00:24:41,560
- I know.
- I know you know.

343
00:24:41,640 --> 00:24:43,520
But does Mr. Gates?

344
00:24:50,120 --> 00:24:52,120
I can't let you
go down this road.

345
00:24:52,160 --> 00:24:54,160
As far that
man-of-war knows,

346
00:24:54,200 --> 00:24:56,800
we're Spanish merchantmen
under attack by pirate raiders.

347
00:24:56,880 --> 00:24:58,480
We order the Ranger to flee,

348
00:24:58,520 --> 00:24:59,960
the Spaniard passes us
to give chase,

349
00:25:00,040 --> 00:25:01,920
and before she realizes her
error, we've got her trapped.

350
00:25:02,000 --> 00:25:03,520
She's got 100 guns.

351
00:25:03,600 --> 00:25:06,200
We do this properly, she'll never
get a chance to use them.

352
00:25:06,280 --> 00:25:07,640
