357
00:25:14,520 --> 00:25:17,240
The Urca. She's here.
Can't you see that?

358
00:25:17,320 --> 00:25:19,520
All I can see is an empty bay,

359
00:25:19,600 --> 00:25:20,960
a guardacosta warship,

360
00:25:21,040 --> 00:25:22,880
and a captain that's lost
his fucking grip on reality.

361
00:25:22,960 --> 00:25:25,000
Guardacosta?
You think that ship's here on patrol?

362
00:25:25,080 --> 00:25:27,360
That she just happened
by this place at this time?

363
00:25:27,440 --> 00:25:28,920
That ship is an escort.

364
00:25:28,960 --> 00:25:30,200
It's the only explanation.

365
00:25:30,280 --> 00:25:32,640
The Urca has no escort.

366
00:25:32,720 --> 00:25:35,440
Was that not the justification
for this entire endeavor?

367
00:25:35,480 --> 00:25:37,640
They altered their plans.
Found a ship they could spare.

368
00:25:38,960 --> 00:25:41,600
I'm taking the Ranger
and I'm leaving.

369
00:25:41,680 --> 00:25:43,880
What did you just say?

370
00:25:43,960 --> 00:25:46,680
I'm gonna weigh anchor
and I'm gonna make a run for it.

371
00:25:46,760 --> 00:25:48,000
If I can keep ahead
of it before dark,

372
00:25:48,080 --> 00:25:49,760
there's just a chance
we can slip away.

373
00:25:49,840 --> 00:25:52,800
Without the Ranger,
I have no chance against that ship.

374
00:25:53,880 --> 00:25:55,600
I know.

375
00:26:00,600 --> 00:26:03,760
So you're deliberately
challenging my authority here?

376
00:26:03,800 --> 00:26:06,080
Deliberately
violating your duty?

377
00:26:07,640 --> 00:26:10,200
My duty?

378
00:26:10,280 --> 00:26:13,760
My duty is to them, not to you.

379
00:26:13,840 --> 00:26:16,040
Although I have
violated it more times

380
00:26:16,120 --> 00:26:17,760
than I can remember
in your defense.

381
00:26:17,840 --> 00:26:19,840
<i>Helped you deceive good men</i>

382
00:26:19,920 --> 00:26:22,520
who put their trust in me
because I was convinced

383
00:26:22,560 --> 00:26:24,440
they would be better off for it.

384
00:26:24,480 --> 00:26:26,600
Well, not here.
Not this.

385
00:26:26,680 --> 00:26:28,600
This is fucking madness.

386
00:26:28,640 --> 00:26:30,160
Mr. Gates, if you
walk through that door

387
00:26:30,160 --> 00:26:31,880
with the intent
of subverting my plans,

388
00:26:31,960 --> 00:26:35,320
I will have no alternative but to interpret
that as an incitement of mutiny.

389
00:26:35,360 --> 00:26:37,840
You think I'm inciting mutiny?

390
00:26:37,880 --> 00:26:40,120
- You are inciting mutiny.
- I'm managing one!

391
00:26:40,200 --> 00:26:42,520
There are men
out there right now

392
00:26:42,560 --> 00:26:43,800
that know about Singleton,

393
00:26:43,880 --> 00:26:46,200
the book, the cook, all of it.

394
00:26:46,280 --> 00:26:49,720
They know. And they mean to see
you hanged for it.

395
00:26:51,720 --> 00:26:53,000
You told them?

396
00:26:53,080 --> 00:26:54,920
After Billy, I just...

397
00:26:55,000 --> 00:26:58,400
I didn't want to believe you could be
capable of doing something like that.

398
00:26:58,480 --> 00:27:00,920
But I couldn't convince
myself that you weren't.

399
00:27:01,000 --> 00:27:05,040
<i>That's when I realized,</i>
<i>this has got to end.</i>

400
00:27:05,080 --> 00:27:06,880
So what, then?

401
00:27:08,520 --> 00:27:11,160
You preside over a trial
that sees me hanged?

402
00:27:13,280 --> 00:27:14,880
No.

403
00:27:14,960 --> 00:27:16,760
We're going to go home

404
00:27:16,800 --> 00:27:19,440
and I will see you
and Mrs. Barlow secreted away

405
00:27:19,480 --> 00:27:21,480
before anybody
knows you're gone.

406
00:27:21,560 --> 00:27:23,920
<i>You're gonna go to Boston.</i>

407
00:27:23,960 --> 00:27:27,040
<i>You're gonna take the pardon
that she's offered you.</i>

408
00:27:27,120 --> 00:27:30,360
And that is the last that you and I will
ever see of each other.

409
00:27:32,560 --> 00:27:33,960
Please.

410
00:27:35,640 --> 00:27:37,240
Please, don't do this.

411
00:27:39,040 --> 00:27:41,120
I'm sorry.

412
00:27:42,360 --> 00:27:43,960
Take a moment.

413
00:27:45,480 --> 00:27:48,440
I'll deal with them.

414
00:28:00,360 --> 00:28:02,480
This is not what I wanted.

