439
00:29:47,800 --> 00:29:49,360
He's asking if the fort
can turn her guns around

440
00:29:49,400 --> 00:29:51,640
and bring them to bear
on the street... on <i>us.</i>

441
00:29:51,680 --> 00:29:55,000
Let's hope whomever's up there is
not mad enough to consider that.

442
00:29:55,080 --> 00:29:57,240
