<i>as anything but tobacco.</i>

480
00:32:41,640 --> 00:32:44,400
Seville regulates
the trade heavily.

481
00:32:47,000 --> 00:32:49,040
Thank you, Mr. Dufresne.

482
00:33:06,360 --> 00:33:08,160
What the fuck did you do?

483
00:33:09,600 --> 00:33:11,160
Spend enough time on an island,

484
00:33:11,200 --> 00:33:14,080
begin to forget there's
a whole world out there.

485
00:33:14,160 --> 00:33:17,360
A world where the rules
are different.

486
00:33:20,960 --> 00:33:24,120
I went out there, found men
who don't know the rules here

487
